title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 10/22 - McLean/Grimm/Martin
description: --Kevin Falness fills in for PA for a Friday Hockey Feast, Wild Assistant Coach Brett McLean talks the Wild win on Tuesday, Mike Grimm previews the Gophers game tomorrow, and Paul Martin checks in and talks Gophers Hockey and his career.
